Chemistry/Pattern version 0.01
==============================

This module implements a generic molecule pattern matching engine.

TODO:
    extract atom and bond tests to methods in the corresponding classes
    allow user-defined test subroutines
    add positive and negative look-ahead
    consider adding * and +

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:
    - Chemistry::Mol

